1. *On* je zaista obdaren velikim *genijem*. (He is truly gifted with great genius.)
2. U njegovom stvaralaštvu se ogleda nezamisliv *genije*. (In his creativity an unimaginable genius is reflected.)
3. Njegovo delo je veliko ostvarenje ljudskog *genija*. (His work is a great achievement of a human genius.)
4. U njegovoj glavi su se rodile najvrednije ideje i *genijalni* planovi. (In his head the most valuable ideas and genius plans were born.)
5. U njegovom umu je bilo zaključano toliko *genijalnosti*. (So much genius was locked in his mind.)